data.description: 50K BELOW TAX APPRAISAL~WOW! THIS STUNNING PROPERTY THAT TICKS RESIDENTIAL, INCOME & COMMERCIAL BOXES with NO RESTRICTIONS and 400FT of frontage on FM 51!  This immaculate, 3.25-acre property, close to town with complete privacy is a must-see to believe. Entering the driveway a welcoming country home beckons with an oversized wrap-around porch, abundant living & family areas, picturesque views, a HUGE garage apartment & oodles of tasteful updates. Property is blanketed by 100+-year old live oak trees. Spacious great room with vaulted ceilings, oversized stone fireplace & meticulously crafted concrete floors. Kitchen has ledger stone & granite accents atop custom cabinetry & commercial gas range. Primary bedroom suite downstairs has ensuite bath with claw-foot tub. Family room upstairs has kitchenette. Apartment could be a vaca-rental AND a 30x50x12 shop, with electric, RV, Boat parking & more! Perfect for entrepreneurs & even a B&B! SO much more! DO NOT ENTER WITHOUT APPOINTMENT!
